notification.template_body:
Hello Library Staff,

A new book dispute report has been filed:

Incident Number: ${record.number}
Date Created: ${record.sys_created_on}
Student ID: ${record.student_id}

Book Information:
- Title: ${record.book_title}
- ISBN: ${record.book_isbn}
- Value: $${record.book_value}

Damage Details:
- Type: ${record.damage_type}
- Level: ${record.damage_level}
- Description: ${record.description}

Incident Date: ${record.incident_date}

Calculated Fee: $${record.calculated_fee}

Action Required:
1. Review the incident details
2. If needed, request additional information from student
3. Approve or reject the claim
4. Process payment or replacement

Please log in to the Academic Resolve system to review this incident:
${record.getURL()}

Best regards,
Academic Book Dispute Resolution System

Dear Student,

Thank you for submitting your book dispute report. We have received your claim and will review it promptly.

Incident Details:
- Report Number: ${record.number}
- Book: ${record.book_title}
- Damage Type: ${record.damage_type}
- Calculated Fee: $${record.calculated_fee}

Next Steps:
1. Library staff will review your report within 2-3 business days
2. You will receive a notification once a decision has been made
3. If approved, you can pay the fee or arrange replacement online

Track Your Claim:
You can check the status of your dispute at any time using your report number: ${record.number}

If you have any questions, please contact the Academic Library at library@acadresolve.edu

Best regards,
Academic Book Dispute Resolution System

Hello Manager,

An incident requires your approval:

Incident Number: ${record.number}
Student: ${record.student_id}
Book Title: ${record.book_title}
Damage Level: ${record.damage_level}

Requested Fee: $${record.calculated_fee}
Justification: ${record.description}

Library Staff Notes: ${record.approver_notes}

Available Actions:
1. Click "Approve" to authorize payment/replacement
2. Click "Reject" to deny the claim
3. Click "Request More Info" to ask for clarification

Review and Decide:
${record.getURL()}

This request requires your attention within 24 hours.

Best regards,
Academic Book Dispute Resolution System

Dear Student,
We have reviewed your book dispute claim for Report #${record.number}.
Decision: NOT APPROVED
Reason: ${record.rejection_reason}
Book Details: - Title: ${record.book_title} - Original Value: $${record.book_value}
If You Disagree: You have 10 business days to appeal this decision by contacting: Academic Library Manager Email: manager@acadresolve.edu Phone: [Contact Number]
To Appeal: Please include: 1. Your incident number: ${record.number} 2. Additional supporting evidence or information 3. Explanation of why you believe this decision should be reconsidered
Incident History: ${record.getURL()}
Best regards, Academic Book Dispute Resolution System

Payment Confirmation

Incident #: ${record.number}
Amount Paid: $${record.calculated_fee}
Payment Date: ${record.sys_updated_on}
Status: CLOSED

Transaction Details:
Book: ${record.book_title}
Student: ${record.student_id}

Your book dispute has been resolved and your account is now clear.

A receipt has been emailed to your registered email address.

Thank you for your prompt payment.

Best regards,
Academic Book Dispute Resolution System
